Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $Var\left(Y\right)=\frac{1-p}{p^{2}}=EY^{2}-E^{2}Y\iff EY^{2}=\frac{1-p}{p^{2}}+\left(\frac{1}{p}\right)^{2}=\frac{2-p}{p^{2}}$
\end_inset


